name: title
Gatto 25mm beam WT 104 wks: Kinematic of 104-week-old WT mice walking on a 25 mm wide beam

name: description
Gatto 25mm beam WT 104 wks: Original SIMI videos, DeepLabCut-tracked videos and csv files of body kinematics of 104-week-old C57BL/6J mice walking on a wide 25 mm beam. Control Group. Individual trials for each mouse are recorded from 8 cameras and metadata for synchronization is stored as *.smp files.
